@startuml 3A_Blog_Post_Lifecycle
title 3-A · Blog Post Lifecycle (UC-T10 to UC-T15, UC-F12 to UC-F17, UC-S10)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Open Blog > New Post;
:Enter title, rich-text content,\ncategory, tags and visibility;
:Optionally upload cover image;

|System|
:Verify tenant status = ACTIVE;
:Validate title, content and visibility;
if (Validation passed?) then (No)
  :Return 422 validation error;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Create BlogPost record;
endif

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
if (Post action?) then (Save Draft)
  |System|
  :Set status = DRAFT;
  stop
elseif (Post action?) then (Publish Now)
  |System|
  :Set status = PUBLISHED;
  :Set published_at = now();
  :Notify eligible fans by in-app/email preferences;
elseif (Post action?) then (Schedule)
  |System|
  :Set status = SCHEDULED;
  :Store publish_at datetime;
  |Scheduled Job Runner|
  :Run Publish Scheduled Posts job;
  |System|
  :Set status = PUBLISHED when publish_at is due;
  :Notify eligible fans;
else (Archive)
  |System|
  :Set status = ARCHIVED;
  stop
endif

|Anonymous Visitor / Registered Fan|
:Browse blog list or open post detail;

|System|
:Apply content visibility strategy\n(PUBLIC / SUBSCRIBERS_ONLY / PAID_ONLY);
if (Fan can access post?) then (No)
  :Show preview and subscription/upgrade prompt;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Render post content;
endif

|Registered Fan|
if (Interaction?) then (Like)
  |System|
  :Require logged-in fan;
  :Create or update like record;
elseif (Interaction?) then (Comment)
  :Write comment;
  |System|
  :Require logged-in fan;
  :Create BlogComment record;
  if (Moderation required?) then (Yes)
    :Mark comment pending/hidden until review;
    |Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
    :Review comment;
    if (Decision?) then (Restore/Approve)
      |System|
      :Set is_hidden = false;
    else (Hide)
      |System|
      :Set is_hidden = true\nand preserve record for audit;
    endif
  else (No)
    :Display comment immediately;
  endif
else (Read only)
  :No interaction;
endif

stop
@enduml
